%N A173847 Number of permutations of 1..n with no adjacent pair summing to n+7.
%C A173847 If a(n,k) is the number of permutations of 1..n with no adjacent pair summing to n+k, then a(n,k) = a(n,k+1) for n+k even.
%F A173847 k = 7; m = max(0,floor((n-k+1)/2)); a(n,k) = Sum_{j=0..m} (-2)^j C(m,j) (n-j)!.
